---
layout: layouts/base.njk
description: "CoCitizen is a volunteer home for open-source civic-tech tools used by democratic organizations worldwide. We steward, document, and deploy tools for election monitoring, cybersecurity training, and civil society coordination."
---

{# Intro — light, typographic, no dark surface #}
<section class="home-intro" aria-labelledby="wordmark">
  <h1 class="wordmark" id="wordmark" aria-label="CoCitizen">
    <span class="wordmark__co" aria-hidden="true">Co</span><span class="wordmark__citizen" aria-hidden="true">Citizen</span>
  </h1>
  <div class="intro-body">
    <p class="lead highlight">
      A volunteer home for open-source civic-tech tools that have been used in production
      across dozens of countries — by election monitors, civil society groups, and
      organizations working in difficult environments.
    </p>
    <p class="lead">
      We didn't build these tools. We maintain them, improve their deployability,
      and keep them accessible to the organizations that need them.
    </p>
    <div class="intro-cta">
      <a href="{{ site.github }}" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View our work on GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Stats band #}
<div class="stats-band full-bleed surface-dark" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats">
